OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy bills to be cut     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fusing government loans     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Soaring household energy bills are     
OL,6, expected to be cut by energy companies 
OL,7, using government-backed loans.         
OL,9,FIt is thought energy bills could be    
OL,10,Ffrozen at their current level for      
OL,11,Froughly 18 months under the plans.     
OL,13,FEnergy firms would use the loans to    
OL,14,Fsubsidise customer payments, with these
OL,15,Frepaid by additions to household bills 
OL,16,Fover the next 10 to 20 years.          
OL,18,FPrime Minister Liz Truss has pledged to
OL,19,F"deliver on the energy crisis" - with a
OL,20,Fprice freeze widely expected.          
